    <h1>The Kissing Rock and the Barranco Wall on Kilimanjaro</h1>
    <p>The iconic Barranco Wall scramble on the Southern Circuit of Mount Kilimanjaro. The Kissing Rock, what to expect at the wall, and how to climb it without panicking.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
      <span>&middot; <a href="/blog">Back to Blog</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
